---

# Type ascription

```scalascript
println((42: Int))
println(("hello": String))
println(((1 + 2): Int) + 1)
val x: Option[Int] = (None: Option[Int])
println(x)
val xs: List[Int] = (Nil: List[Int])
println(xs)
```
